261
00:14:04,800 --> 00:14:07,680
So tonight,
let's talk about heat in prisons.

262
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,440
Let's start
with the obvious question here.

263
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:13,160
If prisons are too hot,
which clearly many are,

264
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:15,680
