265
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:18,400
And that does seem
like a pretty easy fix !

266
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:21,400
But whenever it's brought up,
lawmakers and prison officials

267
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:24,160
