to number one, shall we ?

277
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:55,240
"We don't want to."

278
00:14:55,440 --> 00:14:59,600
Because after you say that, it doesn't
really matter what you say next.

279
00:14:59,680 --> 00:15:01,920
