365
00:19:48,600 --> 00:19:49,760
Maybe just bad chili.

366
00:19:50,200 --> 00:19:53,880
What the fuck ?
First, no one would ever confuse

367
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:57,520
someone having violent convulsions
with having bad chili.

368
00:19:57,800 --> 00:20:00,800
