and it's called Hormel.

369
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:03,320
Show some respect
to that can of bean nightmares.

370
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:07,000
Guessing your wife's heart attack
might be just bad chili

371
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:11,040
