468
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:04,240
These ain't my cars
and I don't really care about 'em.

469
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:09,120
When I ripped
my testicles open with a drill,

470
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:12,400
