you're not gonna get anywhere else.

492
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:25,760
Well, it turns out, wrong.
Because watch this...

493
00:26:26,240 --> 00:26:29,120
You know me, Scott Elder here
from Elder Mitsubishi.

494
00:26:29,720 --> 00:26:31,720
I'm in a pickle.
My doctor told me

495
00:26:31,800 --> 00:26:35,080
