502
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:55,800
Help I'm in a pickle !

503
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:59,640
Dad, your doctor told you to calm
down before your heart explodes.

504
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:00,880
That's striking.

505
00:27:01,000 --> 00:27:04,120
When you see that many screaming
white guys in pickle costumes,

506
00:27:04,240 --> 00:27:07,320
