520
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:48,880
It's Jack Frost, and I'm in
the doghouse. I need cars !

521
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:51,680
We're in the doghouse
and we need cars !

522
00:27:52,080 --> 00:27:55,080
What is that ? I mean,
what is the concept there ?

523
00:27:55,320 --> 00:27:59,640
Do these car dealers think scripts
that bad are worth outsourcing ?

524
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:02,400
"We're in the doghouse
and we need cars ?"

525
00:28:02,520 --> 00:28:05,080
Don Draper would put his cigarette
out on your forehead

526
00:28:05,160 --> 00:28:06,880
