554
00:29:32,560 --> 00:29:35,440
When you look at what he has done
with these pro forma scripts,

555
00:29:35,520 --> 00:29:38,680
you see that he routinely
makes some capital-C choices,

556
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,360
